data.description: Welcome home! This immaculate home is the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. As you step through the front door, you're greeted with an open floor plan, beautiful LVP floors, French-door entry to the study, natural lighting throughout and a fabulous gourmet kitchen for the chef in the family with ample cabinetry, granite countertops and an oversized island. Large master boasts a luxurious ensuite bathroom with walk through shower and soaker tub. Outside you'll find a covered patio and large backyard with lots of room for additional structure or a pool. Amity Estates is a growing community with monthly get togethers, pickleball, extra special Halloween trick or treat and golf cart Christmas parades. Are you ready to call this home?
